AttributeNames.description: Specifies the response elements you wish to receive. To retrieve all attributes, set to All. If no attribute names are specified, returns a list of instances.

EnvironmentId.description: Specify the AWS Elastic Beanstalk environment by ID.

EnvironmentName.description: Specify the AWS Elastic Beanstalk environment by name.

NextToken.description: Specify the pagination token returned by a previous call.
